{
  "id": "adv_group_thrx_01_02",
  "title": "IIIX 01 02",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――八年前",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Eight years ago.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_schoolclass-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "schoolclass-00-noon",
      "startTime": 2.0380972345
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_02/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_02-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "（小さい頃から友達はあまりいなかった）\n（中学に入ってからは、随分酷いいじめも受けた）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I didn't have many friends when I was little.)\n(I was severely bullied in middle school.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 6.6380972345,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_02/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_02-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "（高校でもそんな日々が続くのかと思っていたけど……）\n（でも、そこで私は『あの子』に会った）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(I thought those days would continue in high school‚ but…)\n(But there‚ I met \"her\".)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.3380972345,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_02/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_02-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "（……葉ちゃん）\n（私の、たった一人の親友）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(…You.)\n(My one and only best friend.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.7714305679,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.8380972345
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_livestage-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "livestage-00-noon",
      "startTime": 27.1047639012
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "藤代葉",
      "speakerNameEn": "You",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_02/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_02-fyou001.m4a",
      "text": "美帆ちゃん、このライブ行ってみたいの\n私一人じゃ怖いし……ね、お願い付き合って！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Miho-chan‚ I want to go to this live.\nI'm scared to go alone… Come with me! Please!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.2714305679,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_02/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_02-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "（もともとアイドルが好きなのは、葉ちゃんだった）\n（私は葉ちゃんに付き合って一緒にライブに行っただけ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(You were the one who loved idols.)\n(I just went to lives with you.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.9380972345,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 45.7380972345
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-night",
      "startTime": 46.0047639012
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "藤代葉",
      "speakerNameEn": "You",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_02/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_02-fyou002.m4a",
      "text": "今度、アイドルのオーディションがあるんだって\n美帆ちゃんも一緒に……え、やっぱダメ……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "They're holding an idol audition soon.\nWill you join me‚ Miho-chan…? Oh‚ I guess not…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.5380972345,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "藤代葉",
      "speakerNameEn": "You",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_02/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_02-fyou003.m4a",
      "text": "大丈夫、私はダメでも美帆ちゃんは受かるよ\nだって、美帆ちゃんくらい可愛い子見たことないもん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's okay‚ even if I don't make it‚ you will‚ Miho-chan.\nI've never seen anyone as cute as you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.1714305679,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_02/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_02-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "（……ええ、私も葉ちゃんも）\n（立派にオーディションに受かりましたとも）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(…And so‚ both You and I)\n(passed the audition with flying colors.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.6047639012,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 70.8380972345
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 70.8380972345
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 71.1047639012
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 73.4201963357
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "藤代葉",
      "speakerNameEn": "You",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_02/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_02-fyou004.m4a",
      "text": "うわー、うわー、私達とうとうデビューだよ！\n信じらんない、私達アイドルになるんだよ！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow‚ wow‚ we're finally debuting!\nI can't believe it‚ we're going to be idols!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.3714305679,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "藤代葉",
      "speakerNameEn": "You",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_02/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_02-fyou005.m4a",
      "text": "衣装とヘアメイクも、うん、バッチリ\n私達、なんだか魔法少女に変身したみたいじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The costumes and hair and makeup… yeah‚ they're perfect!\nDon't we look like we've transformed into magical girls?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.4047639012,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "藤代葉",
      "speakerNameEn": "You",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_02/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_02-fyou006.m4a",
      "text": "魔法少女みたいに、私達も\nステージで誰かを幸せな気持ちに出来たらいいね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Like magical girls‚ maybe we can\nmake someone happy on stage.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.2714305679,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "武田美帆子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mihoko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_02/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_02-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "うん。二人でなら、きっと出来るわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes. I'm sure we can‚ together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.9714305679,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00-noon",
      "startTime": 103.6047639012
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_02/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_02-mhk007.m4a",
      "text": "（葉ちゃんと一緒のアイドル活動は楽しかった）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Being idols together with You was fun.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.6047639012,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_02/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_02-mhk008.m4a",
      "text": "（ライブの後には反省会で、何時間でも話し合って……）\n（グランプリで優勝した時は抱き合って泣いたっけ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(We'd spend hours discussing things after our lives‚ in our reflection meetings…)\n(And when we won the Grand Prix‚ we hugged each other and cried.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.5380972345,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_02/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_02-mhk009.m4a",
      "text": "（――もう二度と、あんな日々は来ないけれど）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(――Though those days will never come again.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 117.1714305679,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――二年前。プレタポルテの会議室にて",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――Two years ago‚ at a Pret-A-Porter meeting room.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.1047639012,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 125.2714305679
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 125.2714305679
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "プレタポルテ幹部",
      "speakerNameEn": "Pret-A-Porter",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_02/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_02-prekan001.m4a",
      "text": "やあ、mihoさん\n改めまして、我がプレタポルテにようこそ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hello there‚ miho-san.\nWelcome to Pret-A-Porter!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.7380972345,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "プレタポルテ幹部",
      "speakerNameEn": "Pret-A-Porter",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_02/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_02-prekan002.m4a",
      "text": "これからはmihoの芸名で活動してもらうことだし\n僕もそう呼ばせてもらっていいかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We'll be having you work under the stage name \"miho\"‚\nso would it be alright if I call you that too?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.6714305679,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 138.7047639012
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_02/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_02-mhk010.m4a",
      "text": "もちろんです\nこれからお世話になります、よろしくお願いいたします",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course.\nI look forward to working with you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.3714305679,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 145.1047639012
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_02/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_02-mhk011.m4a",
      "text": "（プレタポルテ……）\n（芸能界の大物の息子が立ち上げた芸能事務所）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(Pret-A-Porter…)\n(A talent agency founded by the son of a big shot in the entertainment industry.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.3380972345,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_02/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_02-mhk012.m4a",
      "text": "（前の事務所も大手だったけれど）\n（なんというか、こちらは派手ね）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "(My previous agency was also a major player‚)\n(but this one is… flashy.)",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.8714305679,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 157.8047639012
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "プレタポルテ幹部",
      "speakerNameEn": "Pret-A-Porter",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_02/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_02-prekan003.m4a",
      "text": "じゃ、早速だけど\n『ⅢX』の他のメンバーを紹介させてもらうよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well then‚ without further ado‚\nlet me introduce you to the other members of \"IIIX\".",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 159.5047639012,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 4200.000000000017,
          "startTime": 163.7047639012
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 163.7047639012
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_02/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_02-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "初めまして、franです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Nice to meet you‚ I'm fran.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 165.0380972345,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 167.5714305679
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "プレタポルテ幹部",
      "speakerNameEn": "Pret-A-Porter",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_02/sud_vo_adv_group_thrx_01_02-prekan004.m4a",
      "text": "fran君は日本とドイツのミックスルーツでね\nパリコレの舞台に立ったこともある、カリスマモデルだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "fran-kun has mixed Japanese and German roots‚\nand she's a charismatic model who's even walked the runway at Paris Fashion Week.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 170.7380972345,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preconference-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preconference-00-noon",
      "startTime": 175.1380972345
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
